	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102862896555418><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=14&mid=102862896555418>charming undead</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=14&mid=102862896555418#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=159924><span id= >Lady mduble</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>127 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Aug 6th 6:30 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.63]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>i have yet to use my charm undead. i was kind of afraid of using it and have the undead break charm and then decide to kick my ass. i dont like losing exp at level 23. i know the experience loss is evan greater at higher levels. so if any of you necros that have charmed undead could you please let me know how long does it last and what is the best way of using this spells.<br><br>One other question ok maybe 2. If you charm a ghoul is he still magic to hit and does he still use his spells.<br><br>any info would be great.<br><br>phleet 23 necro<br>currently in LOIO<br>Torvorniouls server<br><br>PS<br>there is a lot of necro's out there.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
