	   <tr><td colspan=2>This might help you a bit.<br><br>First of all always use darkness. IT is a great friend to the necro. It slows them down and is a dot. Next Fear them and send pet. You might have to attack to. When you cast a dot on an anything. you do full damage when it is rooted, snared or running away from it does less damage when it is attacking you. <br>Learn to fear kit. That is where the true power of the necro comes in. Now some people so lower level pets are not needed i beg to differ. I always get me pet. it is the first spell i buy. if you pets starts to die and you dont have a lot of mana gate the hell out of there. that is what i do. it saves my ass a lot of times. next always buy darkness spells they start to get really good in the 20's. at level 8 buy ward undead. it doers a lot of damage for that level. <br>When you get to level 8 you can start to do the quest for the necro dark book. (it has a name but i forgot what it is) look to see if there is a high level necro around that could help. You need to go buy lava storm then turn left to the fire pit. there is a lot of undead there. some will drop pages 1,2,3,4 they are all no drops when you get all four take them to the 3rd floor of the guild and hail the guy all the way in the back not the first one. and ask what book or something like that he will give you something to put the pages in hit combine and you got yourself the necro book. it has great stats. <br>I always help young necros when i back in the forest we have to look out for our own.<br>When you get to level 12 go to lavastorm by the entrace of nejerna dungon and hunt drakes. i level to 17 there. great exp and money. hope this helps. remember dot,s then fear with pet attacking. you can see the dot killing them.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
