	   <tr><td colspan=2>Aye yes i did mean 1 yellow not blue.&nbsp;&nbsp;You didn't go to the right place in SD.  When you zone into SD from the grey run straight out  until you come to a big platform..  Run up the path, and up there is the good camps..  All con dark blue.  One is a camp of about 14 Sun Revs, and the other is a big camp of Tro jegs.  The ones down on the ground all con light blue to me some even green, but up here is safe and no mob ever wonders up there unless someone trains..  This place is good cuz its nonstop.  I pull with splurt, then get back to pet start attempting to cast snare til its in range to cast, then send pet fear take turns with vexing and cessation..  Wash rinse repeat..  Keep mana skin up at all times, and demi lich up as well..  <br>&nbsp;<br>Sphoenix Darkfever<br>60th Warlock of Terris-Thule</td></tr>
